metadata.name: Mythical Realms
metadata.description: Experience the magic of Ancient Abstract Folk Art with a stunning collection of 444 rare NFTs created by Astra Luman. These unique digital creations will transport you to captivating Mythical Realms, filled with wonder and beauty. Each NFT is one-of-a-kind, and the collection represents a truly special opportunity to own a piece of digital art that's both rare and captivating.
